<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>5912</hymn_number>
<author>mynạ jmyl, mynạ jmyl</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr
 - dạymạ slạmk ạ̉ʿẓm mn kl mkẖạwfy

[V2]
 dạymạ ḥnạnk ạ̉ʿẓm mn jrwḥy

[V3]
 dạymạ klạmk yrfʿny rwḥk yʿzy wysndny

[V4]
 ạ̉nạ nṣrty fy sẖkẖṣk ḥqyqẗ btmlạny

[V5]
 1- ftḥ ʿyny ʿsẖạn ạ̉sẖwfk mʿạyạ sẖddny bạlạ̹ymạn wjwdk kfạyạ

[V6]
 mhmạ ṣʿạby ttḥdy̱ wạlbḥr hạyj mạ byhdy̱

[V7]
 wlạ mwjẗ tqdr ttʿdy̱ ạ̉mr ạlqdyr

[V8]
 2- dmk ygẖṭyny wystr ly ḍʿfy ạ̹nt ạlly tsẖfyny wtrfʿ ʿny dẖnby

[V9]
 mhmạ ʿdwy rạḥ yzạ̉r wfy ḍʿfy ysẖky wyʿyr

[V10]
 ạ̹nt sẖfyʿy ạlly htqdr tḥmyny fyk</lyrics>
<title>dạymạ slạmk</title>
</song>